Class NFRequirement

  • java.lang.Object
    • xml.Requirement
      • xml.NFRequirement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    INFRequirement, IRequirement

    public class NFRequirement
extends Requirement
implements INFRequirement
    Class to hold the NonFunctionalRequirement of the requirement analysis. This class provides JAXB support and can be accessed via the INFRequirement Interface. Getter and Setter must be provided to be JAXB conform. It is implemented in the CustomXMLFormat.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    3852430
    See Also:
    INFRequirement, CustomXMLFormat
